建博客索引页面","content":"默认情况下，应该有一个 (home) 路由组，里面有 <HomeLayout />\n组件。让我们把博客页面放在它下面，这样我们就可以在我们的博客网站上获得漂亮的导航栏。"},"174":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-18","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客索引页面","content":"title: 小提示"},"175":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-19","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客索引页面","content":"像 text-fd-muted-foreground 这样的颜色来自 Fumadocs UI 的设计系统，我们也可以使用自己的颜色，或者使用\nShadcn UI。"},"176":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-20","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客正文页面","content":"请注意，博客文章不会有像 /slug1/slug2 这样的嵌套路径段，我们不需要为博客文章提供包罗万象的路由。"},"177":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-21","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#创建博客正文页面","content":"在 Next.js 中，[slug] 对应的是单层动态路由，[[...slug]] 可选捕获所有路由，这里我们用的是前者。"},"178":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-22","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#write-posts","content":"UI 现在已经完成了，我们可以在 content/blog 目录下写一些博文，比如："},"179":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-23","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs#write-posts","content":"使用 next dev 启动开发服务器后，我们应该会在 /blog 路由下看到博客文章。"},"180":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","type":"page","content":"MDX","url":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx"},"181":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","content":"一种为 Markdown 插入组件的标记语言"},"182":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/mdx","type":"text","ur